description:
Experience a thrilling and erotic story starring Bartleby Montclair of Dresdin, his boyfriend Sonic the Hedgehog, and Sonic's sibs as they travel through Wonderland in an attempt to get home! Comment, rate, and subscribe, and don't forget to punch that bell so you can be notified whenever I upload.

If you're interested in supporting my work, or want to see some exclusive content you can't see anywhere else, be sure to follow my Patreon
www.patreon.com/Tamers12345
